1
00:01:25,520 --> 00:01:26,030
[The Princess Royal]

2
00:01:26,030 --> 00:01:27,890
[Adapted from Mo Shubai's novel,
The Princess Royal]

3
00:01:27,890 --> 00:01:28,950
[on Jinjiang Original Network]

4
00:01:28,950 --> 00:01:30,020
[This is a work of fiction.]

5
00:01:30,020 --> 00:01:33,020
[Episode 4]

6
00:01:34,340 --> 00:01:35,140
Enough.

7
00:01:36,700 --> 00:01:38,260
I can keep him alive,

8
00:01:39,260 --> 00:01:40,380
but he can't escape his punishment.

9
00:01:41,460 --> 00:01:43,180
Decree that Su Rongqing
be subjected to castration.

10
00:01:45,820 --> 00:01:47,220
What have I done

11
00:01:47,460 --> 00:01:49,420
to deserve such protection
from the Princess Royal?

12
00:01:50,180 --> 00:01:51,220
Your great kindness

13
00:01:51,820 --> 00:01:53,220
is beyond my ability
to repay in this lifetime.

14
00:01:54,220 --> 00:01:57,140
You don't have to feel like you owe me.

15
00:01:57,420 --> 00:01:58,380
Rise.

16
00:02:03,660 --> 00:02:04,460
Have you

17
00:02:06,260 --> 00:02:07,540
thought about what you'll do next?

18
00:02:08,340 --> 00:02:09,140
I...

19
00:02:11,980 --> 00:02:13,260
am no longer a real man,

20
00:02:15,060 --> 00:02:15,980
and I'm at a loss

21
00:02:17,740 --> 00:02:19,540
about where to go from here.

22
00:02:25,140 --> 00:02:25,940
Perhaps,

23
00:02:28,260 --> 00:02:29,740
you can stay in my place.

24
00:02:31,660 --> 00:02:32,620
Would you want that?

25
00:02:35,940 --> 00:02:37,060
And think about it,

26
00:02:37,140 --> 00:02:38,460
he didn't leave when you let him go.

27
00:02:39,060 --> 00:02:40,740
Why did he want to stay by your side?

28
00:02:46,340 --> 00:02:47,060
Li Rong,

29
00:02:49,980 --> 00:02:50,860
are you okay?

30
00:02:51,620 --> 00:02:52,820
I did think about the possibility

31
00:02:54,460 --> 00:02:55,380
that he'd want revenge.

32
00:02:57,180 --> 00:03:01,540
No one can forget such an annihilation,

33
00:03:03,460 --> 00:03:05,620
especially not him, once
the most eligible bachelor in Huajing.

34
00:03:11,180 --> 00:03:12,460
I just didn't foresee

35
00:03:15,700 --> 00:03:17,220
that even the deepest bonds

36
00:03:19,300 --> 00:03:21,020
would be overshadowed by political strife.

37
00:03:26,140 --> 00:03:27,220
I was too naive.

38
00:03:44,460 --> 00:03:45,380
So

39
00:03:47,060 --> 00:03:47,980
he made the first move

40
00:03:47,980 --> 00:03:49,900
to administer the slow poison to me

41
00:03:51,140 --> 00:03:52,780
and then took over the power I held

42
00:03:53,780 --> 00:03:55,380
with the guise of eliminating you.

43
00:03:59,060 --> 00:04:00,740
We can't be entirely sure, though.

44
00:04:01,300 --> 00:04:02,660
Perhaps we're both wrong.

45
00:04:02,660 --> 00:04:03,420
Enough said.

46
00:04:04,540 --> 00:04:05,340
I've come to terms with it.

47
00:04:05,540 --> 00:04:07,100
I was killed by Su Rongqing.

48
00:04:07,780 --> 00:04:08,580
Satisfied now?

49
00:04:24,660 --> 00:04:26,100
I warned you

50
00:04:26,660 --> 00:04:29,020
to stay away from him,
but you didn't listen.

51
00:04:29,780 --> 00:04:30,580
See what happens?

52
00:04:30,580 --> 00:04:31,300
You're suffering now.

53
00:04:31,300 --> 00:04:33,020
Pleased to see me suffer, are you?

54
00:04:35,300 --> 00:04:36,540
I didn't mean it like that.

55
00:04:37,580 --> 00:04:39,140
Why must you always challenge me?

56
00:04:45,140 --> 00:04:47,700
Indeed, it happens once in a lifetime

57
00:04:47,700 --> 00:04:48,340
to see the Princess Royal suffer.

58
00:04:48,340 --> 00:04:49,460
How could I not be pleased?

59
00:04:50,140 --> 00:04:51,500
Then you're mistaken.

60
00:04:52,620 --> 00:04:54,580
After all,
he served me for seventeen years.

61
00:04:55,380 --> 00:04:57,300
I willingly accepted death at his hands.

62
00:04:58,180 --> 00:04:58,940
And you,

63
00:04:59,740 --> 00:05:01,420
you're just a bystander
caught in the fire.

64
00:05:01,420 --> 00:05:02,500
What's there for you to gloat about?

65
00:05:02,500 --> 00:05:04,380
Stop talking about it.

66
00:05:04,820 --> 00:05:06,500
The grilled fish is almost ready.
Let's eat.

67
00:05:09,820 --> 00:05:10,500
Here.

68
00:05:14,580 --> 00:05:15,380
Take it.

69
00:05:25,580 --> 00:05:27,500
But let me remind you, Your Highness,

70
00:05:28,740 --> 00:05:30,820
your previous entanglements
with Su Rongqing

71
00:05:31,180 --> 00:05:32,740
would only cause
some physical punishments.

72
00:05:33,260 --> 00:05:35,020
Now, if you keep this up,

73
00:05:35,940 --> 00:05:37,380
you're risking your life.

74
00:05:39,380 --> 00:05:40,300
Your Highness,

75
00:05:40,820 --> 00:05:43,620
the flowers are particularly beautiful
this year.

76
00:05:44,820 --> 00:05:45,620
Meixiang,

77
00:05:46,860 --> 00:05:47,700
do you know

78
00:05:48,820 --> 00:05:51,820
which flowers bloom the brightest?

79
00:05:53,060 --> 00:05:54,060
I do not, my lady.

80
00:05:57,420 --> 00:06:00,820
It's not the phoenix flowers.

81
00:06:03,060 --> 00:06:04,260
It's the thorny ones

82
00:06:05,260 --> 00:06:06,820
that bloom the most brilliantly.

83
00:06:07,600 --> 00:06:09,870
[Mingyue Palace]

84
00:06:13,540 --> 00:06:14,900
Concubine Ning, why did you visit me

85
00:06:14,980 --> 00:06:16,500
in the middle of the night?

86
00:06:17,820 --> 00:06:19,820
It looks like a storm is brewing outside,

87
00:06:20,700 --> 00:06:22,220
and yet you can sleep?

88
00:06:23,340 --> 00:06:25,100
Just don't beat about the bush.

89
00:06:25,900 --> 00:06:26,940
As you know,

90
00:06:27,500 --> 00:06:28,780
I've always lived alone

91
00:06:29,220 --> 00:06:30,940
in Mingyue Palace,

92
00:06:31,900 --> 00:06:33,740
unconcerned with the outside conflicts.

93
00:06:36,060 --> 00:06:37,620
Only you know

94
00:06:38,380 --> 00:06:40,660
whether you're concerned or not.

95
00:06:41,220 --> 00:06:42,580
My nocturnal visit

96
00:06:43,300 --> 00:06:46,860
is to bring you a significant gift.

97
00:06:48,780 --> 00:06:51,580
I'm not sure whether I can bear it.

98
00:06:54,500 --> 00:06:56,740
Prince Su holds the Emperor's favor.

99
00:06:57,100 --> 00:06:59,020
Even the Crown Prince can't rival him.

100
00:06:59,940 --> 00:07:01,660
As Prince Su's mother,

101
00:07:01,860 --> 00:07:03,020
born of humble origins,

102
00:07:03,220 --> 00:07:04,380
have you ever considered

103
00:07:04,460 --> 00:07:06,900
even if the Emperor intends
to make him the Crown Prince,

104
00:07:07,540 --> 00:07:09,020
how could your brother, Xiao Su,

105
00:07:09,020 --> 00:07:10,660
with his mere 20,000 troops,

106
00:07:10,940 --> 00:07:12,060
compete against the Crown Prince

107
00:07:12,060 --> 00:07:15,260
and his mother's powerful

108
00:07:15,900 --> 00:07:18,140
Shangguan family?

109
00:07:20,180 --> 00:07:21,500
You must be kidding.

110
00:07:21,900 --> 00:07:23,940
This whole world belongs to the Emperor.

111
00:07:24,500 --> 00:07:26,660
If the Emperor wishes
to promote my son,

112
00:07:27,780 --> 00:07:29,140
there's no need for contention.

113
00:07:29,820 --> 00:07:31,100
If not,

114
00:07:32,020 --> 00:07:33,580
no one can usurp that position.

115
00:07:33,620 --> 00:07:34,380
Is that so?

116
00:07:35,180 --> 00:07:36,700
Even if Prince Su doesn't vie for power,

117
00:07:36,900 --> 00:07:40,500
the Empress and her clan
will certainly back the Crown Prince.

118
00:07:41,620 --> 00:07:43,420
My family has commanded
the northwestern front

119
00:07:43,420 --> 00:07:45,300
for three generations,

120
00:07:45,620 --> 00:07:47,460
holding significant military power.

121
00:07:49,140 --> 00:07:51,540
With the support of my family's troops,

122
00:07:53,460 --> 00:07:56,100
Prince Su's rise is inevitable.

123
00:07:58,500 --> 00:08:01,580
You just came from the Empress,
didn't you?

124
00:08:07,180 --> 00:08:08,540
Your gift is too big

125
00:08:08,660 --> 00:08:10,020
for me to accept it.

126
00:08:14,220 --> 00:08:15,820
Just by visiting you,

127
00:08:16,300 --> 00:08:17,900
the Empress will grow suspicious.

128
00:08:18,140 --> 00:08:19,700
Given her nature,

129
00:08:20,060 --> 00:08:21,620
she's bound to make a move.

130
00:08:21,820 --> 00:08:22,700
So,

131
00:08:22,780 --> 00:08:26,180
whether you believe me or not
isn't that crucial anymore.

132
00:08:27,660 --> 00:08:28,460
Concubine Rou,

133
00:08:29,980 --> 00:08:30,980
I take my leave.

134
00:08:50,820 --> 00:08:51,780
Are you cold?

135
00:08:59,060 --> 00:09:00,860
It's so cold,

136
00:09:01,340 --> 00:09:02,780
and you gave your coat to me.

137
00:09:03,740 --> 00:09:04,540
How about...

138
00:09:04,820 --> 00:09:05,460
Coming.

139
00:09:08,900 --> 00:09:10,220
Why didn't you say it earlier?

140
00:09:18,460 --> 00:09:19,300
Let me ask you,

141
00:09:21,660 --> 00:09:22,860
have you thought about

142
00:09:24,740 --> 00:09:25,940
seeking out Qin Zhenzhen?

143
00:09:34,060 --> 00:09:35,220
We'll talk about that later.

144
00:09:36,740 --> 00:09:39,460
I thought nothing had changed,

145
00:09:41,220 --> 00:09:42,460
but on reflection,

146
00:09:43,300 --> 00:09:44,620
before we were married,

147
00:09:44,780 --> 00:09:46,700
you had nothing to do with Su Rongqing.

148
00:09:47,540 --> 00:09:48,540
So,

149
00:09:48,940 --> 00:09:50,660
there are still many unknowns.

150
00:09:51,420 --> 00:09:52,660
We'll take it one step at a time.

151
00:09:54,340 --> 00:09:55,420
I have a suggestion for you.

152
00:09:56,220 --> 00:09:57,300
If you're going to intervene,
do it early.

153
00:09:58,140 --> 00:09:59,380
The palace isn't suitable for her.

154
00:10:00,060 --> 00:10:00,980
Don't let her enter the palace.

155
00:10:02,380 --> 00:10:03,340
I see.

156
00:10:05,980 --> 00:10:07,940
But it's rare for you
to say something nice.

157
00:10:11,100 --> 00:10:12,620
You're funny.

158
00:10:13,580 --> 00:10:15,260
Don't you like hearing
something nice from me?

159
00:10:15,540 --> 00:10:17,020
I didn't say that.

160
00:10:18,860 --> 00:10:20,420
I'm just not used to it.

161
00:10:22,100 --> 00:10:23,660
I hadn't planned on saying so.

162
00:10:24,340 --> 00:10:25,420
But I am

163
00:10:25,940 --> 00:10:26,980
a reasonable person.

164
00:10:27,540 --> 00:10:29,620
You came to rescue me,
and even though it backfired,

165
00:10:30,300 --> 00:10:33,060
I still appreciate your effort.

166
00:10:33,940 --> 00:10:37,940
I've indeed made many mistakes,

167
00:10:39,900 --> 00:10:40,860
and I take the blame.

168
00:10:49,300 --> 00:10:50,100
Pei Wenxuan,

169
00:10:52,340 --> 00:10:53,300
let's not discuss

170
00:10:54,100 --> 00:10:55,420
the past anymore.

171
00:10:57,620 --> 00:10:58,780
Can you promise me,

172
00:10:59,340 --> 00:11:00,140
let's not be enemies anymore

173
00:11:01,540 --> 00:11:03,020
right here?

174
00:11:17,940 --> 00:11:18,580
Hurry!

175
00:11:18,580 --> 00:11:20,580
We must evacuate before
the Princess's reinforcements arrive.

176
00:11:20,580 --> 00:11:21,340
Yes.

177
00:11:26,740 --> 00:11:28,340
Your Highness, it's them.

178
00:11:28,500 --> 00:11:29,260
They're the Yangs' men.

179
00:11:29,260 --> 00:11:29,980
Hold them back!

180
00:11:29,980 --> 00:11:30,620
Capture them!

181
00:11:30,820 --> 00:11:31,540
Yes!

182
00:11:31,540 --> 00:11:32,380
Your Highness,

183
00:11:32,380 --> 00:11:34,500
we should focus
on finding the Princess first.

184
00:11:41,060 --> 00:11:44,700
What are your plans next?

185
00:11:45,740 --> 00:11:46,780
I...

186
00:11:49,100 --> 00:11:50,260
I haven't decided yet.

187
00:11:52,020 --> 00:11:54,580
What about you? What are your plans?

188
00:11:58,860 --> 00:12:00,980
I don't want to live like before,

189
00:12:03,780 --> 00:12:05,860
constantly surrounded
by endless suspicion,

190
00:12:06,700 --> 00:12:08,460
witnessing the brutality of Chuan,

191
00:12:10,340 --> 00:12:11,420
or seeing

192
00:12:13,140 --> 00:12:14,820
Su Rongqing's family destroyed.

193
00:12:17,820 --> 00:12:18,420
What about you?

194
00:12:19,300 --> 00:12:21,780
Do you have any regrets from before?

195
00:12:39,020 --> 00:12:39,820
Prince Consort,

196
00:12:40,780 --> 00:12:42,140
you're finally here.

197
00:12:43,140 --> 00:12:44,900
Though you and the Princess
have been at odds for so long,

198
00:12:44,900 --> 00:12:46,340
you both care for each other.

199
00:12:46,900 --> 00:12:48,700
Just bow your head and apologize to her.

200
00:12:48,900 --> 00:12:50,180
Make up with her, please.

201
00:12:52,460 --> 00:12:53,540
She won't understand.

202
00:12:54,020 --> 00:12:55,220
I don't think so.

203
00:12:56,540 --> 00:12:57,980
The Princess is proud,

204
00:12:58,340 --> 00:12:59,540
and there were reasons behind the scenes.

205
00:12:59,740 --> 00:13:01,060
The matter with Concubine Qin,

206
00:13:01,460 --> 00:13:03,020
though she stepped forward
to take responsibility

207
00:13:03,180 --> 00:13:04,180
and helped you out,

208
00:13:04,620 --> 00:13:05,940
people outside are saying

209
00:13:06,020 --> 00:13:07,460
she did it because she was betrayed
by her husband

210
00:13:07,620 --> 00:13:09,380
and had to make this move to save face.

211
00:13:09,980 --> 00:13:13,220
Actually, she just needs a way out.

212
00:13:15,500 --> 00:13:16,700
If it were that simple,

213
00:13:16,700 --> 00:13:17,780
it'd be wonderful. However...

214
00:13:17,780 --> 00:13:18,580
Prince Consort,

215
00:13:18,660 --> 00:13:20,780
sometimes things are really that simple.

216
00:13:20,940 --> 00:13:21,580
Or,

217
00:13:21,780 --> 00:13:23,220
maybe I should go and tell the Princess

218
00:13:23,220 --> 00:13:24,140
you're here to see her?

219
00:13:24,140 --> 00:13:24,860
No need.

220
00:13:28,500 --> 00:13:29,660
It's my fault
for not handling things properly,

221
00:13:29,980 --> 00:13:30,940
and I owe it to the Princess.

222
00:13:32,180 --> 00:13:32,980
It's better

223
00:13:36,820 --> 00:13:37,820
not to disturb her further.

224
00:13:45,100 --> 00:13:45,820
Prince Consort,

225
00:13:46,420 --> 00:13:48,740
there's trouble!

226
00:13:49,380 --> 00:13:50,060
What's happened?

227
00:13:50,460 --> 00:13:51,740
Following the Emperor's decree

228
00:13:51,820 --> 00:13:53,500
to execute the entire Su family,

229
00:13:53,700 --> 00:13:55,380
the Princess tried to save Young Master Su

230
00:13:55,500 --> 00:13:56,860
by pleading in front of the Emperor

231
00:13:56,900 --> 00:13:58,220
and accidentally spoke out of turn.

232
00:13:58,220 --> 00:13:59,380
She's been sentenced to a caning.

233
00:13:59,460 --> 00:14:00,980
I'm worried she won't endure it.

234
00:14:00,980 --> 00:14:02,700
You must come to her rescue!

235
00:14:02,820 --> 00:14:03,500
Hold it.

236
00:14:05,780 --> 00:14:06,460
Thirteen.

237
00:14:07,460 --> 00:14:08,260
Fourteen.

238
00:14:09,220 --> 00:14:10,020
Fifteen.

239
00:14:10,260 --> 00:14:10,900
Stop hitting her!

240
00:14:17,140 --> 00:14:19,780
Your Highness, just apologize
to His Majesty.

241
00:14:19,860 --> 00:14:21,300
Give up on Young Master Su.

242
00:14:21,420 --> 00:14:23,780
If you keep getting beaten,
you'll lose your life.

243
00:14:25,620 --> 00:14:27,340
Why put yourself through this, Li Rong?

244
00:14:30,220 --> 00:14:32,500
Pei Wenxuan, Pei Wenxuan!

245
00:14:34,420 --> 00:14:36,140
I must save Su Rongqing.

246
00:14:40,260 --> 00:14:41,220
I've indeed

247
00:14:44,780 --> 00:14:46,380
had regrets before.

248
00:14:49,660 --> 00:14:50,300
I...

249
00:14:54,260 --> 00:14:55,380
In my life,

250
00:14:56,940 --> 00:14:58,020
I've been loyal to the court

251
00:14:59,100 --> 00:15:00,180
and loyal to the people,

252
00:15:01,900 --> 00:15:02,700
but I've only failed

253
00:15:04,340 --> 00:15:05,620
the Princess Royal.

254
00:15:30,100 --> 00:15:30,740
Your Majesty.

255
00:15:31,460 --> 00:15:32,660
Speak up.

256
00:15:33,100 --> 00:15:34,660
There's trouble with Princess Pingyue.

257
00:15:59,500 --> 00:16:00,300
Pei Wenxuan,

258
00:16:24,020 --> 00:16:25,220
why are you so nervous?

259
00:16:26,780 --> 00:16:27,820
I'm not nervous.

260
00:16:28,620 --> 00:16:31,940
I'm just trying to think
of how to prove my innocence.

261
00:16:32,900 --> 00:16:33,900
What innocence?

262
00:16:40,620 --> 00:16:42,260
I'm thinking about how to tell you

263
00:16:42,260 --> 00:16:43,700
that I did nothing last night.

264
00:16:46,780 --> 00:16:47,700
I know.

265
00:16:48,140 --> 00:16:48,780
If you really did something,

266
00:16:48,780 --> 00:16:50,980
I'd definitely feel it.

267
00:16:53,300 --> 00:16:55,580
Li Rong, you're a princess.

268
00:16:55,580 --> 00:16:56,260
Can't you be

269
00:16:57,060 --> 00:16:58,220
a bit more reserved?

270
00:16:59,340 --> 00:17:01,580
Pretend to be pure at my age? Seriously?

271
00:17:21,860 --> 00:17:22,460
Let's go.

272
00:17:22,460 --> 00:17:22,900
Where are we going?

273
00:17:22,900 --> 00:17:23,700
Not here.

274
00:17:23,780 --> 00:17:24,580
Nothing is found here either.

275
00:17:25,260 --> 00:17:26,220
What are you doing, Pei Wenxuan?

276
00:17:26,220 --> 00:17:27,300
Slow down.

277
00:17:28,420 --> 00:17:29,060
Come here.

278
00:17:30,020 --> 00:17:30,940
Pei Wenxuan,

279
00:17:30,940 --> 00:17:32,220
how did I never notice

280
00:17:32,220 --> 00:17:33,460
you're like a rabbit?

281
00:17:36,740 --> 00:17:37,180
Take this.

282
00:17:37,180 --> 00:17:37,900
What for?

283
00:17:38,020 --> 00:17:38,820
Cover yourself.

284
00:17:43,380 --> 00:17:44,180
Wait.

285
00:17:55,140 --> 00:17:55,740
Su...

286
