331
00:19:51,340 --> 00:19:52,060
Princess.

332
00:19:52,340 --> 00:19:53,180
Scoundrel,

333
00:19:53,180 --> 00:19:54,460
stay away from my sister.

334
00:20:01,820 --> 00:20:03,820
Sister, get on my horse.

335
00:20:04,660 --> 00:20:06,260
