542
00:30:23,660 --> 00:30:24,380
and I

543
00:30:25,460 --> 00:30:26,740
am just a pawn,

544
00:30:27,300 --> 00:30:29,020
whose happiness,

545
00:30:29,140 --> 00:30:31,140
