00:31:37,420 --> 00:31:38,580
can be a bargaining chip,

571
00:31:39,740 --> 00:31:41,020
it should carry more value.

572
00:31:42,340 --> 00:31:43,060
Mother,

573
00:31:44,860 --> 00:31:46,260
you're not cut out to be a politician.

574
00:31:47,500 --> 00:31:50,420
Leave these matters to me and Chuan.

575
00:31:50,780 --> 00:31:51,380
As for you,

576
00:31:52,980 --> 00:31:54,260
you only need to do one thing.

577
00:31:54,700 --> 00:31:56,300
Do you even realize what you're saying?

578
00:31:56,300 --> 00:31:57,500
I've thought this through.

579
00:31:59,380 --> 00:32:00,540
All I need from you

580
00:32:03,060 --> 00:32:04,660
is to truly be a mother.

581
00:32:15,100 --> 00:32:17,300
I just want to survive,

582
00:32:18,100 --> 00:32:19,700
and Chuan needs to survive.

583
00:32:34,700 --> 00:32:35,500
What threat

584
00:32:37,700 --> 00:32:38,860
have the Yangs posed?

585
00:32:39,540 --> 00:32:40,740
If they rebel,

586
00:32:43,180 --> 00:32:45,220
they would implicate Chuan
as the mastermind.

587
00:32:46,340 --> 00:32:47,260
Your father

588
00:32:47,580 --> 00:32:50,660
has always been looking for something
to use against Chuan and your uncle.

589
00:32:55,620 --> 00:32:56,540
I see.

590
00:32:58,540 --> 00:33:00,820
Don't worry. I'll handle it.

591
00:33:01,380 --> 00:33:03,540
If Mother wants to summon Pei Wenxuan,
go ahead.

592
00:33:04,220 --> 00:33:05,300
I'm talking to Chuan now.

593
00:33:15,140 --> 00:33:15,740
Your Highness,

594
00:33:31,980 --> 00:33:32,980
do you think

595
00:33:33,900 --> 00:33:36,620
our marriage should happen again?

596
00:33:40,260 --> 00:33:41,420
Are you feeling sorry for me?

597
00:33:46,900 --> 00:33:48,620
The side hall has been prepared.

598
00:33:48,860 --> 00:33:50,740
You can have a good rest there later.

599
00:33:51,860 --> 00:33:52,500
What's wrong?

600
00:33:52,820 --> 00:33:54,460
Thank you for your kindness,
Your Highness,

601
00:33:55,140 --> 00:33:56,500
but I'm not worthy of it.

602
00:33:59,660 --> 00:34:00,460
Rongqing,

603
00:34:01,780 --> 00:34:03,060
don't degrade yourself like that.

604
00:34:12,660 --> 00:34:13,500
Do you think

605
00:34:15,940 --> 00:34:17,660
I am any different from you?

606
00:34:21,060 --> 00:34:24,580
I once believed Father cherished me,

607
00:34:25,780 --> 00:34:26,820
but in the end,

608
00:34:27,740 --> 00:34:30,180
I was just a pawn he used
to manipulate the noble families.

609
00:34:31,020 --> 00:34:32,940
I thought Mother was wholly
looking out for my best,

610
00:34:33,420 --> 00:34:35,020
but compared to the interest
of the Shangguan family,

611
00:34:35,020 --> 00:34:36,220
I could be discarded at any time.

612
00:34:37,380 --> 00:34:38,540
I believed that man

613
00:34:40,340 --> 00:34:42,700
was sincerely devoted to me,

614
00:34:45,220 --> 00:34:46,220
but his heart

615
00:34:48,020 --> 00:34:49,500
was set on another woman.

616
00:34:52,100 --> 00:34:53,860
I thought the brother I helped to rise

617
00:34:53,860 --> 00:34:55,220
would respect and value me,

618
00:34:55,460 --> 00:34:57,020
but to suppress the noble families,

619
00:34:58,820 --> 00:35:00,380
he didn't hesitate to punish me.

620
00:35:08,460 --> 00:35:09,980
I am alone

621
00:35:13,420 --> 00:35:14,460
and live a life full of hardship

622
00:35:16,700 --> 00:35:17,420
and exhaustion.

623
00:35:22,180 --> 00:35:24,860
Your Highness, there are ways
to help you out.

624
00:35:25,060 --> 00:35:26,180
I don't need to feel sorry for you.

625
00:35:28,100 --> 00:35:29,940
You may be different from the Princess

626
00:35:30,580 --> 00:35:31,940
I used to know.

627
00:35:32,540 --> 00:35:34,540
Starting over and knowing each other again

628
00:35:35,020 --> 00:35:36,020
might not be a bad idea.

629
00:35:40,180 --> 00:35:41,300
You do make a point.

630
00:35:42,900 --> 00:35:43,820
Then let it be so.

631
00:35:46,220 --> 00:35:48,940
I cannot tolerate Your Highness's guest.

632
00:35:51,420 --> 00:35:52,900
Nor can I accept

633
00:35:52,900 --> 00:35:54,500
Mr. Pei's beloved.

634
00:35:56,820 --> 00:35:59,220
It seems we have reached an understanding.

635
00:36:02,140 --> 00:36:04,620
Then, let's settle our marriage.

636
00:36:05,460 --> 00:36:06,820
Let's endure each other.

637
00:36:07,500 --> 00:36:09,660
After a couple of years,
when you hold more power,

638
00:36:09,900 --> 00:36:10,820
we can separate.

639
00:36:13,340 --> 00:36:14,740
Then, we can seek revenge

640
00:36:14,900 --> 00:36:15,780
and settle grievances.

641
00:36:16,980 --> 00:36:18,020
What do you think, Your Highness?

642
00:36:18,700 --> 00:36:21,140
Alright, let's make do for now.

643
00:36:22,140 --> 00:36:24,660
But, if you want to marry me,

644
00:36:25,500 --> 00:36:26,780
you'll have to prove your worth.

645
00:36:27,860 --> 00:36:29,460
If Mr. Pei isn't capable,

646
00:36:29,740 --> 00:36:31,220
I won't stoop to marry you.

647
00:36:33,500 --> 00:36:34,620
Rest assured, Your Highness.

648
00:36:35,740 --> 00:36:37,980
I will certainly ease your burden.

649
00:36:40,180 --> 00:36:42,620
I'm expecting it.

650
00:36:44,340 --> 00:36:44,900
Wait.

651
00:36:45,900 --> 00:36:46,780
What now?

652
00:36:49,340 --> 00:36:52,340
I'd like to ask Your Highness
for a small favor.

653
00:36:53,420 --> 00:36:53,980
Tell me.

654
00:36:54,380 --> 00:36:57,260
Please prepare a lavish carriage for me.

655
00:37:02,500 --> 00:37:05,140
Greetings, Your Majesty!

656
00:37:05,660 --> 00:37:07,900
Long live, Your Majesty!

657
00:37:08,340 --> 00:37:11,340
I summoned you to the side hall.

658
00:37:11,860 --> 00:37:15,180
I assume you understand
what this implies.

659
00:37:17,340 --> 00:37:19,740
You seem somewhat weary,

660
00:37:20,300 --> 00:37:22,260
and I have prepared fresh clothes
for you.

661
00:37:22,940 --> 00:37:23,940
You should return now.

662
00:37:29,900 --> 00:37:31,300
Do you have any grievances?

663
00:37:33,660 --> 00:37:37,260
Your Majesty, if I retreat,

664
00:37:37,740 --> 00:37:39,140
what would become of the Princess?

665
00:37:39,900 --> 00:37:41,580
That's not for you to worry about.

666
00:37:43,980 --> 00:37:46,620
And if I wish to worry?

667
00:37:47,300 --> 00:37:48,340
What are you implying?

668
00:37:48,780 --> 00:37:50,980
Currently, the Yang family
is like a fish out of water

669
00:37:51,100 --> 00:37:52,380
and is merely struggling in vain.

670
00:37:52,780 --> 00:37:54,420
But if the Crown Prince aligns with them,

671
00:37:54,540 --> 00:37:56,620
it would drag him into trouble.

672
00:37:57,380 --> 00:37:58,620
In your opinion,

673
00:37:59,300 --> 00:38:01,260
what should be done now?

674
00:38:01,900 --> 00:38:03,300
Your Majesty and the Crown Prince

675
00:38:03,380 --> 00:38:04,860
only need to do one thing.

676
00:38:06,660 --> 00:38:09,420
Once I leave Qionghua Palace,

677
00:38:09,820 --> 00:38:11,260
seal off any information
about my entrance to the palace

678
00:38:11,540 --> 00:38:13,860
and my time
with the Princess last night immediately.

679
00:38:14,180 --> 00:38:16,980
I have already done so.

680
00:38:18,620 --> 00:38:20,340
But why do you ask this

681
00:38:21,220 --> 00:38:22,260
of me?

682
00:38:24,620 --> 00:38:25,220
Your Majesty,

683
00:38:26,380 --> 00:38:28,540
the Emperor has many eyes and ears
in the palace.

684
00:38:28,660 --> 00:38:30,380
Nothing you do can be hidden from him.

685
00:38:31,260 --> 00:38:32,060
Now,

686
00:38:32,700 --> 00:38:34,180
only if Your Majesty targets me,

687
00:38:34,380 --> 00:38:36,220
can I gain the Emperor's trust.

688
00:38:36,900 --> 00:38:39,180
You're just a minor eighth-rank official.

689
00:38:40,300 --> 00:38:41,860
Why are you willing to be embroiled

690
00:38:42,660 --> 00:38:43,860
in royal intrigues?

691
00:38:47,700 --> 00:38:48,940
If not for ambitious dreams,

692
00:38:49,660 --> 00:38:50,900
why not retire and return home?

693
00:38:53,020 --> 00:38:54,580
Aren't all those in the court

694
00:38:54,980 --> 00:38:57,860
striving for the same thing?

695
00:38:59,220 --> 00:39:00,740
Then why choose the Crown Prince?

696
00:39:02,580 --> 00:39:03,460
I...

697
00:39:04,500 --> 00:39:06,460
cannot bear
to see the Princess humiliated.

698
00:39:11,500 --> 00:39:13,020
You care for my daughter?

699
00:39:17,060 --> 00:39:18,500
I'm eager to assist and protect

700
00:39:19,780 --> 00:39:22,140
Your Majesty and Her Highness.

701
00:39:30,580 --> 00:39:32,580
Mr. Pei, please.

702
00:39:46,380 --> 00:39:47,260
Ultimately,

703
00:39:47,940 --> 00:39:49,660
we can't escape this siege.

704
00:39:54,420 --> 00:39:55,140
Wait.

705
00:39:55,700 --> 00:39:57,140
This isn't the way out of the palace

706
00:39:58,060 --> 00:39:59,980
but towards the Emperor's Imperial Study.

707
00:40:02,420 --> 00:40:03,460
I assume the Emperor

708
00:40:04,100 --> 00:40:06,060
has already heard about what happened
at Qionghua Palace

709
00:40:06,820 --> 00:40:08,140
and is summoning me.

710
00:40:13,580 --> 00:40:16,380
I am Fu Lai,
an attendant by the Emperor's side.

711
00:40:16,540 --> 00:40:17,980
His Majesty wants to meet Mr. Pei.

712
00:40:18,140 --> 00:40:19,060
Please follow me.

713
00:40:26,260 --> 00:40:26,940
Eunuch Fu,

714
00:40:27,420 --> 00:40:29,380
do you know
why His Majesty is summoning me?

715
00:40:30,980 --> 00:40:32,940
Mr. Pei surely has an idea.

716
00:40:40,660 --> 00:40:43,060
Please wait here for a moment.

717
00:40:53,940 --> 00:40:55,020
Major General Yang?

718
00:41:02,900 --> 00:41:04,700
I'm curious as to

719
00:41:04,700 --> 00:41:05,700
why you are here today.

720
00:41:09,780 --> 00:41:10,620
To seek a marriage alliance.

721
00:41:13,020 --> 00:41:15,980
I'm afraid that might disappoint you.

722
00:41:17,660 --> 00:41:20,620
This matter is likely already settled.

723
00:41:21,860 --> 00:41:22,780
What do you mean?

724
00:41:25,260 --> 00:41:27,020
Don't you know

725
00:41:27,220 --> 00:41:28,860
why I turned back last night?

726
00:41:31,020 --> 00:41:33,260
It... was you last night?

727
00:41:33,700 --> 00:41:34,740
Exactly.

728
00:41:36,460 --> 00:41:37,460
I was fortunate indeed.

729
00:41:37,660 --> 00:41:39,060
Not only did I rescue the Princess

730
00:41:39,060 --> 00:41:40,380
from your hands

731
00:41:40,820 --> 00:41:42,780
but also spent the night alone with her.

732
00:41:42,780 --> 00:41:43,780
You're asking for trouble.

733
00:41:44,900 --> 00:41:46,860
Do you intend to resort to violence
in front of His Majesty?

734
00:41:58,260 --> 00:41:59,900
His Majesty is a wise ruler.

735
00:42:00,260 --> 00:42:03,060
You have no reason to be resentful.

736
00:42:03,940 --> 00:42:06,500
Perhaps you should return to the Northwest.

737
00:42:07,180 --> 00:42:08,700
I hear the silk there

738
00:42:09,180 --> 00:42:10,340
is particularly fine.

739
00:42:12,820 --> 00:42:14,980
The silk is used for funerals
in the Northwest.

740
00:42:14,980 --> 00:42:16,340
You dare curse me?

741
00:42:16,660 --> 00:42:17,740
Sorry to let you down.

742
00:42:19,140 --> 00:42:21,340
But I was the designated
Prince Consort candidate.

743
00:42:23,780 --> 00:42:25,020
There was a hiccup last night,

744
00:42:25,220 --> 00:42:27,300
and His Majesty commanded me
to return immediately.

745
00:42:27,780 --> 00:42:29,140
You're served as a stepping stone

746
00:42:29,140 --> 00:42:31,060
to pave the way for me and the Princess.

747
00:42:34,420 --> 00:42:38,380
Yang Quan, Pei Wenxuan,
enter the hall now!

748
00:42:54,340 --> 00:42:55,780
I, Pei Wenxuan.

749
00:42:55,940 --> 00:42:57,060
I, Yang Quan.

750
00:42:57,580 --> 00:42:59,300
Wish Your Majesty well.

751
00:43:00,780 --> 00:43:02,100
Pei Wenxuan, rise.

752
00:43:05,700 --> 00:43:06,780
Thank you, Your Majesty.

753
00:43:07,340 --> 00:43:10,300
I, Yang Quan, wish Your Majesty well.

754
00:43:12,620 --> 00:43:13,700
What are you doing here?

755
00:43:13,980 --> 00:43:14,860
Your Majesty,

756
00:43:15,580 --> 00:43:18,220
I have come today
to seek a marriage alliance.

757
00:43:19,740 --> 00:43:20,540
Oh?

758
00:43:21,180 --> 00:43:22,100
Whom do you wish to marry?

759
00:43:22,940 --> 00:43:25,420
I am fond of Princess Pingyue.

760
00:43:25,860 --> 00:43:27,300
Your Majesty, please grant your approval
for our marriage.

761
00:43:33,300 --> 00:43:35,540
Pingyue is my eldest daughter,

762
00:43:36,220 --> 00:43:37,940
and her marriage is no trivial matter.

763
00:43:39,380 --> 00:43:41,540
Let me give this further thought.

764
00:43:42,740 --> 00:43:43,420
Pei Wenxuan,

765
00:43:43,900 --> 00:43:45,620
come walk with me in the garden.

766
00:43:45,740 --> 00:43:46,380
Yes.

767
00:43:48,900 --> 00:43:49,620
Your Majesty,

768
00:43:51,060 --> 00:43:52,620
Major General Yang is still kneeling.

769
00:43:54,380 --> 00:43:55,060
Rise.

770
00:43:55,380 --> 00:43:56,820
If you have nothing else to say,
you may leave now.

